flowchart TD

%% =========================
%% Initialization
%% =========================
A[Start Script] --> B[Initialize PLECS<br/>clc + warnings]

%% =========================
%% Configuration
%% =========================
B --> C[Load Configuration<br/>RESULTS_DIR<br/>HOLD / CLEAR / SAVE flags]

%% =========================
%% Data Definition
%% =========================
C --> D{mapvars_dim == 3?}

D -->|Yes| E[Build 3D Data Structure]
D -->|No| F[Build 2D Data Matrix]

E --> G[Define simStruct]
F --> G

%% =========================
%% Model & Scopes
%% =========================
G --> H[Get Current Model]
H --> I[Extract Model Name]
I --> J[Load Scope List]

%% =========================
%% Clear Traces
%% =========================
J --> K{CLEAR_TRACES?}
K -->|Yes| L[Clear All Scope Traces]
K -->|No| M[Skip Clearing]

L --> N[Prepare Results Directory]
M --> N

%% =========================
%% Directory Setup
%% =========================
N --> O{SAVE_TRACES?}
O -->|Yes| P[Create RESULTS_DIR + Scopes_Traces]
O -->|No| Q[Skip Directory Creation]

P --> R[Print Timestamp + Model Info]
Q --> R

%% =========================
%% Main Loop
%% =========================
R --> S[Start Simulation Loop<br/>for sim = 1:N]

S --> T[Print Iteration Header]

T --> U[Assign Parameters<br/>from data(sim,:)]
U --> V[Log Parameter Values]

V --> W[Run Simulation<br/>plecs simulate]

%% =========================
%% Hold Traces
%% =========================
W --> X{HOLD_TRACES?}
X -->|Yes| Y[Hold Trace in All Scopes<br/>Iteration_i]
X -->|No| Z[Skip Holding]

Y --> AA[Next Iteration]
Z --> AA

AA --> AB{More Iterations?}
AB -->|Yes| S
AB -->|No| AC[Exit Loop]

%% =========================
%% Save Traces
%% =========================
AC --> AD{SAVE_TRACES?}
AD -->|Yes| AE[Save Traces per Scope]
AD -->|No| AF[Skip Saving]

AE --> AG[Print Completion Summary]
AF --> AG

%% =========================
%% End
%% =========================
AG --> AH[End Script]